\frametitle{Contributions}

\textit{"Does a live state graph for Kubernetes and predefined traversal tools improve the quality, speed and interpretability of Root-Cause-Analysis under dynamic cluster conditions compared to snapshot-based approaches."}

\vspace{30pt}

\begin{itemize}
  \item Live-state graph approach under dynamic conditions
  \item Introduction of LLM-friendly and interpretable traversal interface
  \item Design of RCA-Dataset for Kubernetes
  \item Derives recommendations for future AI-based RCA-Systems
\end{itemize}

